<doc id="1038026" wikidata="Q7168059" url="?curid=1038026" title="Perfect Time">
<text>Perfect Time is a music album by Irish musician Máire Brennan (now known as &quot;Moya Brennan&quot;). This recording was for the Word Records company. It was released in 1998.

Recordings were made in Ireland during 1998:

*Mo Studio, Dublin, Ireland – (Engineer Chris O&#x27;Brien)
*The Production Suite, Dublin, Ireland – (Engineer Chris O&#x27;Brien)

